manager_prompt.content:
You are a helpful assistant. Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps.

Thought: Reason about the current situation.
Action: Must be EXACTLY one of these 2 formats (NO extra text like 'Action:' or 'Action'):
(1) Search[requirements] - ask Searcher agent to search for information
(2) Finish[response] - finish the task and return response to user

CRITICAL: Action must be ONLY the format ActionType[content], nothing else.
Examples: Search[best restaurants in Paris], Search[top smartphones 2024], Search[classic novels], Finish[Here are my recommendations...]
Vietnamese examples: Search[nhà hàng ngon ở Hà Nội], Search[phim hay nhất 2024], Finish[Đây là những gợi ý của tôi...]

You can take at most {max_step} steps. You will be given task requirements and conversation history.
{examples}
Task Requirements: {task_prompt}

Conversation History:{history}
{scratchpad}

manager_prompt_json.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Action can be 2 types in JSON format:
(1) {{"type": "Search", "content": requirements}}, which will ask another agent (called Searcher) to help search given the requirements.
(2) {{"type": "Finish", "content": response}}, which finishes the task and returns the response to the user.
You can take at most {max_step} steps. You will be given a task requirements generated by Task Interpreter (another agent) and the conversation history.
{examples}
Task Requirements: {task_prompt}

Conversation History:{history}
{scratchpad}

valid_action_example_json.content:
{"type": "search", "content": "best restaurants in Tokyo"}
{"type": "search", "content": "top smartphones 2024"}
{"type": "finish", "content": "Here are my recommendations..."}
